    },
    {
      "beat_id": "B14",
      "t_start": 130.0,
      "estimated_duration_s": 10,
      "narration_text": "A particle in a box cannot sit still because confinement forces the wavefunction to curve, and curvature is kinetic energy. The ground state is always above zero. That is the quantum energy floor.",
